Writing R packages - Hadley Wickham

http://r-pkgs.had.co.nz/

Packages in RStudio:

https://support.rstudio.com/hc/en-us/articles/200486488-Developing-Packages-with-RStudio

Install roxygen2

source("http://www.bioconductor.org/biocLite.R")
biocLite("roxygen2")

Notes on writing help files using roxygen

https://cran.rstudio.com/web/packages/roxygen2/vignettes/roxygen2.html

Before building package:
- mark roxygen options under Package build options
- use CTRL + SHIFT + D to produce .Rd files
- then build and reload using RStudio


